        </div>
        <blockquote class="testi-quote">
          The AGM financial report used to take me half a day to prepare. With Dominium I generate it in under 5 minutes — it's audit-ready and completely professional. The committee was very impressed.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="testi-metric">5-minute AGM reports</div>
        <footer class="testi-author">
          <div class="testi-avatar">JC</div>
          <div>
            <span class="testi-name">Joseph Camilleri</span>
            <span class="testi-role">HOA Administrator, Msida Court — Msida</span>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stats-social { background: var(--white); }

  /* ── Stats bar ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .stats-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
    padding: var(--sp-6) var(--sp-8);
    background: var(--navy);
    border-radius: var(--r-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-16);
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--lime);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: rgb(255 255 255 / .55);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-div {
    width: 1px;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / .1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .stat-div { display: none; }
    .stats-bar { gap: var(--sp-6); }
  }

  /* ── Testimonials grid ───────────────────────────────── */
  .testi-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--sp-6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .testi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  /* ── Card ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .testi-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    padding: var(--sp-8);
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
    border-radius: var(--r-2xl);
    transition: all var(--t-slow);
  }

  .testi-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--navy-100);
    box-shadow: var(--sh-xl);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .testi-stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    color: var(--lime-dark);
  }

  .testi-quote {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--slate-700);
    line-height: 1.75;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .testi-metric {
    display: inline-flex;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    background: var(--navy-50);
    padding: var(--sp-2) var(--sp-4);
    border-radius: var(--r-full);
    border: 1px solid var(--navy-100);
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .testi-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    padding-top: var(--sp-5);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--slate-100);
  }

  .testi-avatar {
    width: 2.75rem;
    height: 2.75rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--lime);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .testi-name  { display: block; font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark); }
  .testi-role  { display: block; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--slate-500); line-height: 1.4; }
</style>
